7. COMPLIANCE

Licensee shall comply with:
a) Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA)
b) Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA)
c) Applicable provincial privacy laws
d) Canadian electronic commerce laws
e) All security and privacy requirements specified by Estate Kit Inc.

8. TERM AND TERMINATION

8.1 This license is effective until terminated.

8.2 Estate Kit Inc. may terminate this license immediately if Licensee:
